{"id": "nos022", "name": "Cam_St136_695_11_13", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_02"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Hi~\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... What are you doing here?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Dragging you to the classmate reunion, obviously.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "I'm just about to go there right now. Bug off.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "... Huh, that's unexpected. I was so sure that you wouldn't attend an event like this.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... What kind of class holds a reunion three months after graduation?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "The whole class graduated without a hitch. Your attendance rate also just barely passed the requirement. It's something worthy of celebration~ Come on, be happier!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Sidenote, why did you come all the way to my home just to fetch me? Isn't your home closer to the venue?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "As class rep, it is my responsibility to ensure that everyone is present!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Tch...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Everyone, is it?</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\nI still... can't get in contact with Aroma.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...... Oh.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Every time I try to see her, I always get stopped by her sister. She doesn't even answer my phone calls.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Her sister changed her number. She said that this is the most important time period for Aroma.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Yeah... must be really tough to be an idol...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Didn't you...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...... Nothing.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "... I miss the time we spent together, especially on the roof. We would eat lunch there together, prepare for tests together... Sometime, you would secretly smoke there and get yelled at by Iris. I really want to go back to those times...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... You know very well that's impossible.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Yeah... Iris moved to a place far away too.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "No, even before that. Ever since Aroma's car accident...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "... I'm not going to the reunion after all.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Eh? But we're almost there...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "I have nothing to say to those people.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "Hey! Where are you going?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "I'm going to grab a drink myself. Sorry 'bout that, class rep. We can't get everyone to attend, to begin with.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...? What are you doing?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "I'm going with you.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Huh? You do realize you're the organizer, right?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "We can't get everyone to attend, to begin with...\nBesides, drinking alone sounds way too pathetic, isn't it? Two people drinking together sounds much better, right? \nOr do you have nothing to say to me as well?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">On the other hand, I do have a lot of things I want to say to you...</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "So you're going to skip the event you organized yourself... That's so unlike you.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "We've already graduated. I'm tired of being that model student crap too...\nRight now, I just want to be a friend that can chat about the good old times.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "That's not what you said just minutes ago...\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "... Then, how about I treat you? Will you be more willing to let me go with you?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "Nah, it's fine... We can split the bill.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "You've grown taller again.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_02"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "やっほ～\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……何やってんだよ、こんなところで。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "誰かさんを同窓会に引っ張っていくために来たの。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "今行こうとしてたんだよ。うぜぇな。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……へぇ、意外。絶対来ないと思ってたけど。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……卒業して3か月で同窓会って、バカなんじゃねぇの。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "全員無事卒業できたし、あんたの出席日数もぎりっぎりで通過できたし！\nお祝いしなきゃでしょ！\nほら！もっと嬉しそうにしなよ！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "てかなんで俺ん家の前まで来てるんだよ。\nお前、遠回りだろ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "学級委員長として、全員出席させるのは私の義務ですから！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "ッチ……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……全員ね。</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\nやっぱり……Aromaには連絡がつかなかった。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……へぇ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "会いに行っても、お姉さんに止められちゃうし。\n電話もつながらない。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "あいつの姉貴が電話番号換えたんだろ。\n今がAromaにとって大事な時期だから～とか言って。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "うん……芸能人になるって……大変だね……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "お前……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……なんでもねぇ。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……一緒に過ごしてた時期が懐かしいね。\n屋上でさ、一緒にご飯食べて、テストの準備して……\nあんたはたまにコッソリあそこでタバコ吸ってた。\nで、Irisに怒られて……\nあの頃に戻りたい……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……そんなの無理だってとっくに分かってただろ。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "うん……Irisも、遠くに引っ越しちゃったしね。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "いや、もっと前からだよ。\nAromaが事故に遭ってからだ……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……やっぱ行くのやめた。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "え？でももうすぐそこ……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "あいつらと話すことなんかねぇし。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "ちょっと！どこ行くわけ？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "一人で飲みに行く。\n委員長悪いな。\n元々、全員集まるなんて無理な話だったんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "私も行く。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "はぁ？お前幹事だろ。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "元々、全員集まるなんて無理な話だったんでしょ……\nそれにぼっち酒なんて可哀想すぎだし。\n2人の方がまだマシでしょ？\nそれとも、私とは話すことなんかない？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">私はあんたと話したいことたくさんあるけどね……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "自分で企画したイベントバックレるなんてらしくねぇな……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "もう卒業したし、模範生には疲れてたんだよね……\n今は過去のことを語り合えるただの友達がいい。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "さっきと言ってること違くねぇ……？\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……じゃあ、私のおごり。\nこれで友達になりたくなった？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "いいよ……普通に割り勘で。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "あんたまた背のびたんじゃない？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_02"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗨～\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……妳在這邊幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "拖你去同學會啊。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我現在正要去啦，煩死了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……真意外，還以為你一定不會出席的。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……哪有畢業三個月就辦同學會的班級啊。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "全班都順利畢業，你的出席日數也低空飛過，這是值得慶祝的事啊～開心點啦！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "說起來幹嘛特地跑來我家樓下堵我啊？妳家過去不是更近嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "身為班長，我有必要確保每個人都要到！\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "呿……\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……每個人嗎？</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n我還是……聯絡不到 Aroma。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……喔。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "每次去找她，都被她姊姊給擋下來，連電話也打不通。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "她姊幫她換的，她說現在是 Aroma 最重要的時期。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯……成為偶像真是不容易呢……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "妳不是……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……沒事。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……我好懷念我們在一起的時候，尤其是頂樓，我們在那邊一起吃午餐、準備考試……你有時候在那裡偷抽煙，還會被 Iris 罵。好想回到那個時候……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……早就不可能了吧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯……Iris 也搬去好遠的地方了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "不，在更早之前，自從 Aroma 出車禍後……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……果然我還是不去了，同學會。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "咦？都快到了……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我跟那些人沒什麼好聊的。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喂！你要去哪？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我要自己去喝一杯。抱歉啦班長，本來就沒有辦法每個人都到的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……？妳幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我跟你去。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "吭？妳是主辦耶？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "本來就沒有辦法每個人都到的嘛……\n而且一個人喝酒聽起來太可悲了吧？兩個人一起不是比較好嗎？還是你跟我也沒什麼好聊的？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我倒是有很多想跟你聊的……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "居然想蹺掉自己辦的活動……不像妳啊。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我們已經畢業了，我也當累了什麼模範生……我現在只想當個可以聊聊過去的朋友。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "妳剛剛不是這麼說的啊……\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……不然我請客，你會比較想讓我跟嗎？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "不用啦……各付各的就好了。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "你又長高了耶。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_02"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "하이~\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...여긴 왜?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "너 동창회 끌고 가려고 왔지.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "안 그래도 지금 막 가는 중이었다고. 귀찮게 진짜.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "...의외네? 절대 참석 안 할 줄 알았는데.\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...졸업하고 3개월에 한 번씩 동창회 하는 반이 세상에 어딨냐.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "반 전체가 무사히 졸업했잖아! 출석일수도 간당간당했던 너까지 무사히 졸업했으니, 얼마나 잘 된 일이야? 그러니 조금은 즐거워하라고!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "그런데 왜 우리 집까지 온 거야? 동창회 장소 너네 집에서 훨씬 가깝잖아?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "옛 반장의 권한으로 모든 인원 전부 확실하게 참여시키려고 그랬지!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "하아...\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...모든 인원이라...</font>\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n난 아직도... Aroma랑 연락이 안 돼.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...아...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "걔 찾으러 갈 때마다, 항상 걔 언니가 막아섰잖아. 전화도 안 되고.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "번호는 진작에 바꿨겠지. 지금 Aroma에게 가장 중요한 시기라고 했으니깐.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "응...아이돌이 된다는 건, 정말 쉽지 않은 일이야...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "너는...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...아무것도 아니야.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "...우리 함께 했을 때가 그립다...특히 옥상에서의 일들. 같이 점심도 먹고 시험도 준비하고... 넌 거기서 몰래 담배 피우다가 Iris한테 욕도 먹고 그랬잖아. 정말이지 그때로 돌아가고 싶어...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...그럴 가능성은 이미 옛날에 사라져버렸어.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "응... Iris도 멀리 이사가 버렸으니깐.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "아니. 그보다 더 전에. \nAroma가 교통사고를 당하고 나서부터...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...동창회...역시 가지 않는 게 좋겠어.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "뭐? 이미 거의 다 왔는데...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "그 친구들이랑 별로 하고 싶은 얘기도 없어.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "야! 어디 가?\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "그냥 혼자 한잔하러 가련다. 미안하다, 반장. 사실 처음부터 모두가 함께 하는 그런 동창회는 이미 없던 거나 다름없어.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "...? 응? 왜?\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "나도 같이 갈래.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "뭐? 동창회 주최자가 빠지면 어떡해!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "어차피 모두가 다 참여하는 그런 동창회도 아니잖아...그리고 혼술이라니, 딱하기도 해라. 두 사람이면 더 낫지 않을까? 아니면 너도 나한테 별로 하고 싶은 얘기가 없는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">난 너랑 하고 싶은 이야기 많은데...</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "네가 주최하고 만든 모임을 이렇게 내팽개치다니... 너답지 않다.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "우린 이미 졸업했다고. 나도 모범생 역할이라던가 이런 피곤한 거 그만하고 싶다고... 지금은 그저, 같이 이야기 나누고 들어줄 수 있는 그런 친구가 되고 싶을 뿐이야.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "아까 전에 했던 말이랑 완전 다른 것 같은데...\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "...아니면 내가 쏠게. \n이러면 마음이 조금 바뀌려나?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "됐어...그냥 더치 하자.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos2201"], "content": ""}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "키가 또 큰 것 같네.\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_02"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗨～\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……妳在這邊幹嘛？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "拖你去同學會啊。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我現在正要去啦，煩死了。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……真意外，還以為你一定不會出席的。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……哪有畢業三個月就辦同學會的班級啊。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "全班都順利畢業，你的出席日數也低空飛過，這是值得慶祝的事啊～開心點啦！\