l"], "content": "……没事。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……我好怀念我们在一起的时候，尤其是顶楼，我们在那边一起吃午餐、准备考试……你有时候在那里偷抽烟，还会被 Iris 骂。好想回到那个时候……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……早就不可能了吧。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "嗯……Iris 也搬去好远的地方了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "不，在更早之前，自从 Aroma 出车祸后……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……果然我还是不去了，同学会。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "咦？都快到了……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我跟那些人没什么好聊的。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "喂！你要去哪？\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "我要自己去喝一杯。抱歉啦班长，本来就没有办法每个人都到的。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……？妳干嘛？\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我跟你去。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "吭？妳是主办耶？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "本来就没有办法每个人都到的嘛……\n而且一个人喝酒听起来太可悲了吧？两个人一起不是比较好吗？还是你跟我也没什么好聊的？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我倒是有很多想跟你聊的……</font>\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "content": "居然想跷掉自己办的活动……不像妳啊。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Clara"], "content": "我们已经毕业了，我也当累了什么模范生……我现在只想当个可以聊聊过去的朋友。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Daniel"], "c